experience.description:
Main responsibilities: 
•	Management of construction and installation works for the construction of Automotive Gas Filling Compressor Stations (SAFE equipment);
•	Interaction with customer service of PJSC GAZPROM, customer technical supervision service and with state authorities (GOS, Rostechnadzor);
•	Management of the staff of full-time employees, hired brigades and subcontractors;
•	Technical supervision of construction and installation works;
•	Development of technological regulations, instructions, technological maps;
•	Confirmation of the completed scope of work, verification of the forms of KS-2, KS-3;
•	Registration of reporting documentation, welding works log, assembly, general work log.

The company ICA Construction, is the general contractor for the construction of the WHSD (Western high-speed diameter, 5th turn). 
Objects: 
	•	Direct management of the construction process at the facilities;
•	Management of the staff of full-time employees, hired brigades and subcontractors;
•	Ensuring fulfillment of construction tasks, targeted and rational use of resources, execution of construction plans, reconstruction, plans for commissioning of construction projects, delivery of the facility to the Customer; 
•	Development of technological regulations, instructions, technological maps;
•	Registration of reporting documentation, welding works log, assembly, general work log.
Achievements: 
•	Growth to the position of the chief of the construction site;
•	Under my leadership, the following objects were completed: Bridge at the mouth of the rivers Middle
Nevka and Bolshaya Nevka; Overpass on the approach to the bridge at the mouth of the rivers Middle Nevka and Bolshaya Nevka; 
The works were delivered on time (the president of the Russian Federation participated in the opening); 
•	Successful testing of the facility and delivery to ROSTEKHNADZOR;
•	Optimization of works (reduction of resources for work performance).
